Netflix Homepage Replica
This project is a replica of the Netflix homepage, showcasing HTML and CSS skills to recreate the layout and design of the Netflix website. The project includes responsive design elements and utilizes Font Awesome for icons.

Files Included:
netflix.html: The main HTML file containing the structure of the Netflix homepage.
style2.css: The CSS file providing styles for the HTML elements.
logo.png: Image file for the Netflix logo.
tab-content-1.png, tab-content-2-1.png, tab-content-2-2.png, tab-content-2-3.png: Image files used within the tab content section.
main.js: JavaScript file for potential future interactivity (not included in the provided code).
How to Use:
Clone or download the repository to your local machine.
Open index.html in a web browser to view the Netflix homepage replica.
Explore the different sections of the homepage, including the header, tabs, tab content, and footer.
Features:
Responsive design ensuring compatibility with various screen sizes and devices.
Accurate representation of the Netflix homepage layout, including navigation, hero section, tabs, tab content, and footer.
Use of Font Awesome for icons.
Custom CSS styles to mimic Netflix's aesthetic and branding.
